notes: This is a piano arrangement of 「Only」, the ending song for the anime パーティーから追放されたその治癒師、実は最強につき.
Note that this arrangement is pitched 2 semitones above the original (the original is in the key of G).
The composer is Shunryu and the original arranger is Fujinaga Ryutaro (Elements Garden).
You can hear the original song here.
